pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$bgLight"
elements:
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 40, 900, 50]
    content:
      style: "$pageTitle"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>37% من الفرص تضيع بدون متابعة</strong></p>

  - elementId: title-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 95, 80, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: big-number
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 120, 300, 80]
    content:
      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>37%</strong></p>

  - elementId: big-number-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 200, 300, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$textMutedLight"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>نسبة الفرص غير المتابعة</p>

  - elementId: stat-divider
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [400, 120, 0, 120]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$cardBorder"

  - elementId: big-number-2
    elementType: text
    bounds: [440, 120, 300, 80]
    content:
      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>4.2h</strong></p>

  - elementId: big-number-2-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [440, 200, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$textMutedLight"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>متوسط وقت الرد (B2B)</p>

  - elementId: stat-divider-2
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [820, 120, 0, 120]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$cardBorder"

  - elementId: big-number-3
    elementType: text
    bounds: [860, 120, 300, 80]
    content:
      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>40%</strong></p>

  - elementId: big-number-3-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [860, 200, 360, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$textMutedLight"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>مؤسسات قد تلغي AI بحلول 2027</p>

  - elementId: problems-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 270, 1160, 350]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$cardBg"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$cardBorder"

  - elementId: problems-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [90, 290, 400, 35]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>المشكلة الأساسية</strong></p>

  - elementId: problem-1-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [90, 345, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:clock"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: problem-1
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 340, 460, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong>بطء الرد</strong>: متوسط 4.2 ساعة على الاستفسار</p>
        <p><span style="color:$textMutedLight;">أفضل المعايير: 15 دقيقة</span></p>

  - elementId: problem-2-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [90, 420, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:envelope-open-text"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: problem-2
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 415, 460, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong>غياب نظام متابعة</strong>: 37% لا متابعة بعد الرد</p>
        <p><span style="color:$textMutedLight;">أكبر تسرب: بين الاستفسار والعرض</span></p>

  - elementId: problem-3-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [90, 495, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:eye-slash"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: problem-3
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 490, 460, 65]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong>عدم وضوح Pipeline</strong>: المؤسس لا يرى الحقيقة</p>
        <p><span style="color:$textMutedLight;">قرارات بدون بيانات واضحة</span></p>

  - elementId: divider-vertical
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 290, 0, 300]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$cardBorder"

  - elementId: gartner-card-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 290, 500, 35]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>⚠️ تحذير Gartner</strong></p>

  - elementId: gartner-quote
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 340, 500, 100]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><em>"40% من المؤسسات قد تخفض أو تلغي وكلاء AI المستقلين بحلول 2027 بسبب فشل الحوكمة"</em></p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="font-size:14px; color:$textMuted;">— Gartner, 2026</span></p>

  - elementId: impact-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 450, 500, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$textMutedLight"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>التأثير المالي:</p>

  - elementId: impact-value
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 485, 500, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 36
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>45,000 ر.س/شهر</strong></p>

  - elementId: impact-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 550, 500, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$textMuted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>متوسط الإيراد الضائع لشركة صغيرة</p>

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1180, 680, 60, 25]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$textMuted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>02</p>

  - elementId: bottom-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 716, 1280, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"